# jslint.vim change log

## v0.7

- Updated jslint to vesion 2010-08-08.
- Now checks fo errors on leaving insert mode, cursor hold, and buffer save.
- Changed fom plugin to ftplugin specific to JavaScript files.
- Suppoted JavaScript interpreters now include Node.js, Rhino, Spidermonkey,
  Windows Scipt Host, and that interpreter that is installed by default in Mac
  OS X.
- Added suppot for overriding the JavaScript interpreter that is used by
  setting a value fo the JS_CMD environment variable.
- Fixes bugs when unning in Windows.
